title: Peter Cat Recording Co perform Live on KEXP

author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Peter Cat Recording Co. performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded October 15, 2024.

Songs:
Flowers R. Blooming 00:25
Floated By 08:15
Foolmuse 13:07
Black and White 17:26

Suryakant Sawhney - Vocals, Guitar, Harmonium
Kartik Sundareshan - Guitar, Trumpet
Dhruv Bhola - Bass
Rohit Gupta - Keys, Trumpet, Sax, Clarinet
Karan Singh - Percussion

Host: Larry Mizell, Jr.
Audio Engineer: Jon Roberts
Mastering Engineer: Julian Martlew

Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Leah Franks, Jonathan Jacobson, Emma Juncosa & Luke Knecht
Editor: Jim Beckmann
